  • Constructor Details

    • Project

      public Project(String type, double budget, String start, String end, String title, String customer, double size, boolean isRenovation, String isPublished)
      Project's parent constructor. Sets up values every project type include.
      Parameters:
      type - which type of project is.
      budget - available budget for this project.
      start - project's custom start date.
      end - project's custom end date.
      title - unique title of the project.
      customer - customer of the project.
      isRenovation - if this construction is a 'New Build' or a 'Renovation'.
